===Nagazi===
====The Nagazi Guild====
Nagazi is the shortened (name) version of The Nagazi Guild, which is a PvP Guild based in the rpg game Neverwinter Nights, and Neverwinter Nights 2.


====Nagazi (Shepherd Dog)====
'''Nagazi''' is a [[Georgian language|Georgian]] word meaning  ''Shepherd Dog'' 

Usually the word is used to refer to the Caucasian Shepherd Dog ("kavkasiuri nagazi" in Georgian) which is sometimes mistakenly named "Ovcharka" ("Shepherd Dog" in Russian).

